ChangeLog for Version 2.4
</p>
<ul>
<li>Add User Management</li>
<li>Add Admin Realms to policies, to allow better policies in bigger setups</li>
<li>Add API key, that can be used for accessing /validate/check</li>
<li>Load PSKC Token seed files.</li>
<li>Add more sophisticated logging. Severe errors via Email</li>
<li>WebUI: Registrtion token can be enrolled in WebUI</li>
<li>WebUI: The token seed can be displayed in WebUI after generation</li>
<li>WebUI: Only the token types that are allowed to be enrolled are displayed</li>
<li>WebUI: Login_Mode Policy: Disable access to WebUI for certain users</li>
<li>WebUI: Add reload button in Audit view</li>
<li>SQLResolver: The Where statement is used in all cases</li>
<li>SSH-Token Application: Only fetch keys of the requested user</li>
<li>Apache client can work with several hosts on one machine</li>
<li>Documentation: Tokentypes and Supported Hardware Tokens</li>
<li>Improve RADIUS module</li>
<li>WebUI: Fix download of audit log</li>
<li>Fix missing access right of user to GET /caconnector</li>
</ul>

